            <h4 class="m-termmisc">CUSTOM SAUNAS</h4>
            <p class="mterms-disc-ee">Shipping &amp; tax are not included in any custom sauna order. When we invoice for the sauna, it is solely for the sauna itself. Initially, the design hasn't even been approved. Once the design is approved and the sauna is manufactured, we can weigh it and send it to the trucking company to determine the shipping cost. Both tax &amp; shipping must be paid before we can dispatch any custom saunas. Since we ship out many saunas, we typically receive wholesale prices on shipping.</p>
            <br>
