            <p class="mterms-disc-e">Custom &amp; commercial saunas are non-refundable due to the involvement of 3D designers and various professionals from the design phase to engineering and blueprint creation. We have to hire a team of people to design each custom &amp; commercial sauna which takes hundreds of hours. Because each custom &amp; commercial sauna requires significant time and resources, there are no refunds for custom &amp; commercial saunas after 24 hours from the time the order is placed because we have already contracted a team of professionals to start working on the blueprint of your sauna. 
            </p>
